I"ï,<h1 id="science-park-albert-einstein">Science Park Albert Einstein</h1>

<p>The conference will take place in the Science Park Albert Einstein. The Science Park is located on the Telegrafenberg in Potsdam. It is home to astrophysical, astronomical, meteorological and geophysical observatories of the instituts AIP, AWI, DWD, GFZ, and PIK, which are integrated into an English country garden, which was already designed in the 19th century.</p>

<p><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/17/Signboard_of_the_Wissenschaftspark_Albert_Einstein.JPG/320px-Signboard_of_the_Wissenschaftspark_Albert_Einstein.JPG" alt="" />
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/36/Einsteinturm_7443.jpg/320px-Einsteinturm_7443.jpg" alt="" />
<a href="/assets/pdf/conf2019/deRSE_Campusplan.pdf"><img src="/assets/img/conf/deRSE_Campusplan.png" alt="Campusplan" /></a></p>

