<h3 id="parking">Parking</h3>

<p>On the grounds of the Science Park can not be parked. Please use the parking facilities in Potsdam city center, e.g. the parking garage at the main station.</p>

<h3 id="tickets-in-long-distance-traffic">Tickets in long-distance traffic</h3>

<p>We offer together with the DB an event ticket. Booking is via: <a href="https://bahn.events.ccc.de/">https://bahn.events.ccc.de/</a></p>

